a.n: The Escort 2: Lilly Love, Dana DeArmond & Tyler Nixon

p.k: When a beautiful young woman enters the escorting profession, she's put off by her first client. But under the tutelage of a smart and capable madam, she quickly learns the ropes of the world's oldest profession, and realizes that there is a little charm and romance under his macho exterior. A SweetSinner film.
